{"tid":1321320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新城市之殤] 要小心新鴻基啲公關工作","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:05:04.000Z","uid":75514,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3bedb2daeb5c19ac4ca69e5a911b2c47a2e49e31","tid":1321320,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇留意，新鴻基啲商場一直以嚟負面新聞好似比較少咁<br />\n唔係因為佢哋做得好，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而係識得打傳媒關係，等記者唔好寫咁多衰嘢</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n事實係新鴻基啲商場根本好多問題<br />\n倒如新城市個戲院又拆又起成十年有多<br />\nMK新世紀廣場又係裝修足十年咁滯<br />\n<br />\n但點解少負面新聞？因為有能力同做功夫叫記者唔好報咁多負面新聞囉<br />\n<br />\n今次新城市咁樣比狗入，一時三刻肯定多人嘈<br />\n但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">相信新鴻基都係會用一貫公關手段，透過影響傳媒，等佢哋少啲繼續報，慢慢淡化事件</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁可以點做？就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">迫/引新鴻基繼續爆公關災難，然後以後有咩少少衰嘢都唱行佢，等啲傳媒唔報唔得</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢需要各位巴絲守望相助，大家努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a22f016d391ad0ef1e6737148b13f77602576e3","tid":1321320,"uid":125680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"b2dc33302f5b93df3057781554380e424c545f05","tid":1321320,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2aa3989f39e93a7505d4e3439adcd44143b5a5c","tid":1321320,"uid":20477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2284a8aceeb27ca89d4d437e8ec5890625745a9","tid":1321320,"uid":235727,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"新鴻X Marketing頂級<br />\n你見啲垃圾地段樓盤都可以包裝到豪宅咁樣就知"},{"pid":"d6023c24890327c27e7e5c3b2bd6622632ea9217","tid":1321320,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2284a8aceeb27ca89d4d437e8ec5890625745a9","tid":1321320,"uid":235727,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"新鴻X Marketing頂級<br />\n你見啲垃圾地段樓盤都可以包裝到豪宅咁樣就知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:16:58.000Z","msg":"手段係好過大部份同行<br />\n地產霸權污名又由誠哥食晒"},{"pid":"2ee743e326c17ff49734f80ecc4de635d0aa9171","tid":1321320,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d2d34aba25925513fa4a3bceaa1e6530e7a6dc","tid":1321320,"uid":222360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2503285ecfb340fa29d3ce5a6a3512fea77ae36d","tid":1321320,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936b83ee5b9a64d3a7b83327667ae71030633f77","tid":1321320,"uid":214051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T18:54:51.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"f3f2050342ae49d0a3044955b657a8a0dee0d56c","tid":1321320,"uid":5996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d2d34aba25925513fa4a3bceaa1e6530e7a6dc","tid":1321320,"uid":222360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b144aa392e079f40af03fecc2be241e50b0cd373","tid":1321320,"uid":